<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Taska - Password Reset Successful</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #10b981;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            color: #10b981;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .success-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d1fae5 0%, #a7f3d0 100%);
            border: 2px solid #6ee7b7;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .success-box h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #065f46;
            font-size: 22px;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #f0fdf4;
            border-left: 4px solid #10b981;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info-box h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #10b981;
        }
        .info-box ul {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #10b981;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #059669;
        }
        .warning-box {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border-left: 4px solid #d97706;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .warning-box strong {
            color: #b45309;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">✓ Taska - Password Updated</div>
        </div>

        <p>Hello <strong>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</strong>,</p>

        <div class="success-box">
            <h3>✅ Password Successfully Reset!</h3>
            <p>Your Taska account password has been successfully updated.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>📋 Details:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</li>
                <li><strong>Reset Time:</strong> {{resetTime}}</li>
                <li><strong>Account Status:</strong> Active & Secure</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 16px;">You can now log in to your account with your new password and get back to managing your tasks.</p>

        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="https://taska-rho.vercel.app/login" class="btn">Sign In to Taska</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>🔐 Security Best Practices:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>✅ Your new password is strong and secure</li>
                <li>✅ Consider enabling two-factor authentication</li>
                <li>✅ Keep your password confidential</li>
                <li>✅ Log out from all devices if needed</li>
                <li>✅ Review login activity on your account</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="warning-box">
            <strong>⚠️ Didn't reset your password?</strong>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0;">If you didn't initiate this password reset, your account may be at risk. Please:</p>
            <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                <li>Change your password immediately</li>
                <li>Review your account activity</li>
                <li>Contact our support team right away</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div style="background-color: #f3f4f6; border-radius: 5px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;">
            <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Ready to boost your productivity?</strong></p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">Start organizing your tasks and achieve your goals with Taska!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated confirmation from Taska.</p>
            <p>Questions? Contact our support team - we're happy to help.</p>
            <p>&copy; 2026 Taska. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>🚀 Smart Task Management</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 